org.apache.jena.vocabulary

Class XSD

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.vocabulary.XSD

  • public class XSD
extends Object
    Defines Jena resources corresponding to the URIs for the XSD primitive datatypes which are known to Jena.
